entries.description: Add UNKNOWN state to RemediationExecutionState and add IN_PROGRESS/EXITED/UNKNOWN states to RemediationExecutionStepState.
Add MinBitrate for QVBR mode under H264/H265/AV1 output codec. Add GopBReference, GopNumBFrames, SubGopLength fields under H265 output codec.
Added support for cross-account Active Directories.
Add a utils-lite package that wraps threadlocal meant for internal shared usage across multiple applications across multiple applications

entries.category: AWS SDK for Java v2 Migration Tool
entries.description: General availability release of the AWS SDK for Java v2 migration tool that automatically migrates applications from the AWS SDK for Java v1 to the AWS SDK for Java v2.

entries.category: Amazon Bedrock Agent Core Control Plane Fronting Layer
entries.description: Add tagging and VPC support to AgentCore Runtime, Code Interpreter, and Browser resources. Add support for configuring request headers in Runtime. Fix AgentCore Runtime shape names.
This release adds a persistent connection field to UserPhoneConfig that maintains agent's softphone media connection for faster call connections.
Model whitespace change - no client difference
Update invalid character handling documentation for SQS SendMessage API
